thread.title: Lauren S

author: Lauren S
title: Lauren S
text: Personally found Snapfish great - had a photobook made up for a family members birthday which they were over the moon with. Certainly can't complain about the quality of the prints myself...and this is taking into consideration lots of the pictures were very old and I was warned they may turn out pix elated due to the quality of the originals: they appeared absolutely fine. Would use their services again.
